Colorset 101 fg Black bg White

Style "NERVBarIcom" Sticky, NoTitle, !Handles, !Borders, !Iconifiable
DestroyModuleConfig NERVBarIcom: *
*NERVBarIcom: DrawIcons true
*NERVBarIcom: Dontshow "FvwmIconMan"
*NERVBarIcom: PlainButton up
*NERVBarIcom: FocusButton up
*NERVBarIcom: SelectButton up
*NERVBarIcom: FocusAndSelectButton up
*NERVBarIcom: TitleButton up
*NERVBarIcom: IconButton up
*NERVBarIcom: ReliefThickness 1
*NERVBarIcom: Relief 1
*NERVBarIcom: ButtonGeometry x30
*NERVBarIcom: Font "xft:Sans:Bold:pixelsize=12:minispace=True:antialias=True"
*NERVBarIcom: SelFont "xft:Sans:Bold:pixelsize=12:minispace=True:antialias=True"
*NERVBarIcom: StatusFont "xft:Sans:Bold:pixelsize=12:minispace=True:antialias=True"

DestroyFunc onNERVClicked
AddToFunc onNERVClicked
+ I Popup mnuStartup Root 206p 0
+ C Nop
+ H Nop
+ M Nop

Style "NERVBar" NoTitle, !Handles, !Borders, Sticky, WindowListSkip, \
  CirculateSkip, StaysOn, FixedPosition, FixedSize, !Iconifiable
DestroyModuleConfig NERVBar: *
*NERVBar: Geometry 205x768+0+0
*NERVBar: Rows 60
*NERVBar: Columns 1
*NERVBar: Frame 1
*NERVBar: (1x5, Back #FC0 Icon banner.png Action(Mouse 1) `onNERVClicked`)
*NERVBar: (1x52,Back #CCC Top Swallow "NERVBarIcom")
*NERVBar: (1x3, Swallow "xclock" "exec xclock -digital -update 1 -strftime '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'")

